---
title: Housing Choice — Tours (Phase 1)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor T as Tenant
    participant A as Housing Choice App
    participant S as Team
    actor L as Landlord/PM
    Note over T,S: The app owns the phone number. Every call/text flows Tenant to Team and Landlord to Team THROUGH the app (both directions).<br/>Notes marked [AUTO] are app automation. [MANUAL] is a person (Team) acting.
    Note over T,L: Picks up from Sending Unit — the tenant said YES to touring a specific unit. The tenant STAYS in searching (no placement yet). The tour is tracked as its own tour record (tenant and unit), off any placement.

    Note over S,A: Schedule the tour and arm the reminders.
    S->>A: Record the tour date/time on a new tour record (same-day possible)
    Note over A: [AUTO] Arm the tour-reminder ladder (texts) for this tour — re-arms or cancels if the tour moves
    A->>T: [AUTO] Booking-confirmation text
    A-->>T: [AUTO] Day-before and morning-of reminders (fire on schedule)

    Note over T,L: Route by the tour_process on the property (captured at landlord onboarding).
    alt Self-guided — lockbox
        Note over S,L: Self-tour via a lockbox the landlord provides — Team gates it on a photo ID (no vendor integration).
        S->>A: Ask the tenant for a photo ID before the tour window
        A->>T: Deliver the ID request
        T->>A: Photo ID (picture message, MMS)
        A->>S: Relay the ID — Team reviews it in the thread
        Note over A: [MANUAL] Review the photo ID. NO ID, NO code — ever
        S->>A: Send the lockbox access code
        A->>T: Deliver the access code
    else Landlord-led — group text
        Note over S,L: Team finds a mutual time with the tenant and the landlord separately, then unites them.
        S->>A: Confirm a time with the tenant
        A->>T: Propose and confirm the time
        S->>A: Confirm the landlord/PM will show the unit
        A->>L: Propose and confirm the time
        Note over A: [MANUAL] Form the masked relay group (a pool number) for this tour — Tenant, Landlord, Team. Created now during searching, not tied to a placement
        A->>T: [AUTO] Intro message naming everyone connected
        A->>L: [AUTO] Intro message naming everyone connected
    else Property-management team
        Note over S,L: Coordinate the slot through the PM system (their own process).
        S->>A: Book the slot per the PM process
        A->>L: Confirm the slot with the PM
        A->>T: Share the confirmed tour details
    end

    A->>T: [AUTO] Day-of nudge — text me when you are on the way
    alt Tenant tours
        T->>A: On my way
        A->>S: Relay
        Note over T,L: Tenant tours the unit (self-guided via the code, or the landlord/PM shows it).
        Note over A: [MANUAL] Log the tour outcome on the tour record (toured)
    else No response / no-show
        Note over A: [AUTO] No on-the-way text and no outcome logged — proactive check-in
        A->>T: Everything ok? Want to reschedule?
        alt Reschedule
            T->>A: Yes — reschedule
            A->>S: Relay
            Note over A: [MANUAL] Move the tour → [AUTO] cancel and re-arm the reminder ladder
        else Drops off
            Note over A: [MANUAL] Log a no-show outcome on the tour record
        end
    end

    Note over S,A: Post-tour — collect feedback (Phase-1 — Team-manual).
    S->>A: What did you think? Want to move forward?
    A->>T: Deliver the feedback ask
    T->>A: Feedback
    A->>S: Relay the feedback
    Note over A: [MANUAL] Record the feedback and tour outcome on the tour record
    alt Yes — move forward
        Note over T,S: Hand off to Post-Tour and Application (separate) — the placement (case) is created THERE, not here.
    else No — not a fit
        Note over T,L: Re-match — the tenant stays searching. Hand back to Sending Unit (share a new property, restart the loop).
    end
